# React Native / UI

## Source of truth

- Structure & tabs: `docs/Project_Structure.md`
- Builders, nesting, lock/review: `docs/Template_Builders.md`
- Tokens & chrome: `docs/Styling.md`

## Conventions (from those docs)

- Tabs live in `HomeScreen` (`useState` stacks) — no React Navigation yet.
- Shared chrome first: `Screen`, `ScreenHeader`, `Button`, `TextField`, forms under `src/components/forms/`.
- Style with RN `StyleSheet` + `src/theme/tokens.ts` / `formTokens.ts` — no Tailwind/NativeWind; no arbitrary colors when a token exists.
- Nest: Session → Block → Sequence → Exercise. Internal **cluster** = Sequence.
- Library opens use `reviewMode` (root locked until unlock). Bottom nav hides on builders.
- Session/Block/Sequence: label-first; Name/Brief in More panel. Exercise: inline name search.
- Test layout in Expo Go; respect safe areas, keyboard, and touch targets.
- Fonts: Fraunces (wordmark), DM Sans (UI). Warm dusk palette; cool accents only for Block/Sequence rails/pills.
